      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.2043756323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "見て見て！　みんなすっごく盛り上がってるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2043756323,
      "endTime": 77.3148063975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.5178900716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私達の正体はバレていないみたいね。芽衣がこの名前で\n登録した時は、どうなるかと思ったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5178900716,
      "endTime": 87.1028784749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.305962149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "意外と気付かれないものだな。アイドルが変装する時に\nサングラスをする理由がよく分かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.305962149,
      "endTime": 94.1964610732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.3995447473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルがつけるサングラスは、絶対にバレない\n魔法の変装アイテムなのかもしれないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3995447473,
      "endTime": 101.1812456444,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16737.121919399997
